      </div>

      <div
        class="col-12 col-sm-8 offset-sm-2 offset-md-0 col-md-6 col-lg-4 xp-3 text-justify block-light"
      >
        On a coloured background images with no outlines sometimes work better
        so outlines are optional. {# Mock up a SI document #}
        <div class="my-3 px-3 pt-2 pb-3 text-left">
          <div class="text-larger"><strong>Sailing Instructions</strong></div>
          <div class="d-flex">
            <div style="width: 32%" class="mr-3">
              Class A{% signalFlag 'a' %}
            </div>
            <div style="width: 48%">Class 1{% signalFlag 'n1' %}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="d-flex mt-2">
            <div style="width: 32%" class="mr-3">
              Shorten course{% signalFlag 's' %}
            </div>
