            <div style="width: 32%">b. Penalty{% signalFlag 'red' %}</div>
            <div style="width: 32%">c. Report{% signalFlag 'blackwhite' %}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="col-12 col-sm-8 offset-sm-2 col-md-6 offset-md-3 col-lg-4 offset-lg-0 xp-3 text-justify block-light"
      >
        As well as rectangular flags, all images are available in the square
        shape used in the United States. {# Mock up a SI document #} {% set
        options = { outline: true, viewBox: { default: [180, 180], swallowtail:
        [180, 180], pennant: [240, 180] , triangle: [180, 180] } } %}
        <div class="my-3 px-3 pt-2 pb-3 text-left" style="background: #fff">
          <div class="text-larger"><strong>Sailing Instructions</strong></div>
          <div class="d-flex">
            <div style="width: 24%" class="mr-3">
              Class A{% signalFlag 'a', options %}
            </div>
            <div style="width: 24%">Class 1{% signalFlag 'n1', options %}</div>
          </div>
          <div class="d-flex mt-2">
